      <title>南非团结政府各政党支持经济快速增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/south-africa-unity-government-parties-back-rapid-economic-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非非洲人国民大会和民主联盟在组建所谓的民族团结政府的协议中承诺实现“快速、包容和可持续”的经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/south-africa-unity-government-parties-back-rapid-economic-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 11:49:07 GMT</pubDate>
