    <item>
      <title>德国试图阻止或降低欧盟对中国电动汽车征收的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/germany-trying-to-prevent-or-soften-eu-tariffs-on-chinese-evs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，德国政府正在努力阻止欧盟对中国电动汽车征收的新关税生效——或者至少在无法全面停止的情况下放宽关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/germany-trying-to-prevent-or-soften-eu-tariffs-on-chinese-evs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 04:31:15 GMT</pubDate>
